      Speech
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Chatham House speech: Liz Truss sets out vision for values-driven free trade
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">International Trade Secretary Liz Truss delivers the keynote speech at Chatham House’s ‘Global Trade Live’ event setting out her vision for UK trade policy </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 29 October 2020
</div>

      <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata__other">
        <dl data-module="track-click">
            <dt class="app-c-publisher-metadata__term">
              From:
            </dt>
