                  <a class="govuk-link" href="/government/organisations/department-for-international-trade">Department for International Trade</a> and <a class="govuk-link" href="/government/people/elizabeth-truss">The Rt Hon Elizabeth Truss MP</a>
                </span>
            </dd>
        </dl>
      </div>
